<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("partials/head") %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <!-- Theme toggle button for portfolio page -->
      <div style="position: absolute; top: 24px; right: 24px;">
        <button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle theme">
          <svg class="icon icon-sun" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
          <svg class="icon icon-moon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-hero">
        <img
          src="/HeadShot/IMG_0622 2.jpg"
          alt="Srinath Shrestha"
          class="portfolio-avatar"
        />
        <h1 class="portfolio-name">Srinath Shrestha</h1>
        <p class="portfolio-title">C/C++ &middot; Systems Programming &middot; Program Internals</p>
      </div>

      
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <div class="portfolio-card">
          <p class="about-content">
            I'm fascinated by the full lifecycle of a program &mdash; from source code through
            compilation, to ELF binaries, linking, loading, and execution on the CPU.
            I care about simplicity and understanding systems at their fundamentals.
            I know my way around C, GDB, lldb, Valgrind, and Make.
            Outside of code, I learn and write about what I'm exploring on my <a href="/blogs">blog</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-section">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="portfolio-grid">
          <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h3>Priso – Scene Description Language</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>A scene description language with built-in editor for 2D/3D rendering of simple objects using <span class="tech-highlight">OpenGL</span></li>
              <li>Built from scratch in <span class="tech-highlight">C</span>: <span class="tech-highlight">lexer</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">parser</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">renderer</span>, and editor UI</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/srinathshrestha/priso" class="project-link">View on GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h3>2D Car Racing Game</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Classic arcade-style racing game built in <span class="tech-highlight">C</span></li>
              <li>Custom graphics rendering and assets</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/srinathshrestha/c-Game" class="project-link">View on GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="portfolio-card">
            <h3>ShortURL – Link Analytics Platform</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Self-hosted <span class="tech-highlight">microservices</span> for URL shortening and analytics — you can download and use it too</li>
              <li>Tracks clicks by country, device, and referrer with dashboard</li>
              <li>Stack: <span class="tech-highlight">Go</span> (API Gateway, Auth, Link), <span class="tech-highlight">Python</span> (Analytics, Reports), <span class="tech-highlight">PostgreSQL</span>, <span class="tech-highlight">Redis</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/srinathshrestha/shortURL" class="project-link">View on GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-section">
        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <div class="portfolio-card">
          <div class="experience-item">
            <h3 class="experience-title">Backend Developer Intern</h3>
            <p class="experience-company">SkyForge System Solutions</p>
            <p class="experience-duration">Jan–May 2025</p>
            <p class="experience-description">
              Built production backend for Heliosensium (AI parenting agent). Integrated Neon DB,
              Pinecone, and secure payments; deployed on Render.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="experience-item">
            <h3 class="experience-title">Full Stack Developer Intern</h3>
            <p class="experience-company">LinkVerse</p>
            <p class="experience-duration">May–July 2025</p>
            <p class="experience-description">
              Automated PDF certificate generation (Next.js + Puppeteer), 100+ uses. Developed AWS
              CloudFormation utilities for an AI DevOps agent.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-section">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="portfolio-card">
          <p style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; opacity: 0.6;">Systems</p>
          <div class="tech-stack" style="justify-content: flex-start; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            <span class="tech-tag">C</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">GDB</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Valgrind</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Make</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">x86 Assembly (learning)</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; opacity: 0.6;">Web (Previous)</p>
          <div class="tech-stack" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Next.js</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Express.js</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">AWS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-section">
        <h2>Currently Studying</h2>
        <div class="portfolio-card">
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; line-height: 2;">
            <li>CS:APP &mdash; <em>Computer Systems: A Programmer's Perspective</em></li>
            <li>K&amp;R C &mdash; <em>The C Programming Language</em>, Kernighan &amp; Ritchie</li>
            <li>OSTEP &mdash; <em>Operating Systems: Three Easy Pieces</em></li>
            <li><em>Hacking: The Art of Exploitation</em> &mdash; Jon Erickson</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-section">
        <h2>Connect</h2>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="mailto:srinathshrestha9890@gmail.com" class="social-link">Email</a>
          <a href="/portfolio" class="social-link">Portfolio</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/srinathshrestha" class="social-link">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/srinath-shrestha-584171204/" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <p>Built with hands &copy; <%= year %>.</p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
